{"tid":1747408,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"投票「四要四不要」 - 李碧華","createTime":"2019-11-23T07:57:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-24T00:38:39.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a874db6a86a6a44b1c49df05f4266f651eb733c0","tid":1747408,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T07:57:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20191123/20811634/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191123%2F20811634%2F&d=SNVPshlwtiHAgFu1pF0TpCLieoVo5Z%2Bt8AyiqwqBN0Y%3D&h=b1ffd246\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191123%2F20811634%2F&h=4a58710b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20191123/20811634/</a><br />\n<br />\n投票「四要四不要」 - 李碧華<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20191123/large/1574416400_97f5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20191123%2Flarge%2F1574416400_97f5.jpg&h=dabd275b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中共政治文宣靠口號，簡單易記易洗腦，如什麼「三大紀律八項注意」、「兩個凡是」、「五講四美三熱愛」、「一不怕苦，二不怕死」&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n所以面對11.24那危危乎可能遭奸人發功而告吹的區選，港人記得「四要四不要」。<br />\n<br />\n★四要：──<br />\n<br />\n（一）要早起。最好上午便關注權利和義務。我以前多是晚上才投，不行！通宵工作至7點半投票，施施然吃個早餐倒頭大睡，便放心。大批大陸大媽惡棍黑幫，等着周日下午大破壞，我們當然早着先鞭！<br />\n<br />\n（二）要認清目標。網上或蘋果都有詳盡名單，泛民、建制、鎅票黨、扮獨立人士、騙名人支持、忽然民主&hellip;&hellip;你心中有數。<br />\n<br />\n（三）要看重每一票：都有作用，有價值，眾志成城。<br />\n<br />\n（四）要孝順。這天同父母一起投票，若他們住老人院，便早些取回身份證接去飲茶逛街談天，別讓獻世派利用。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n★四不要：──<br />\n<br />\n（一）不要有任何投票以外的活動，勇和均公告完全不會堵路開花示威──若這樣幹肯定是卧底。<br />\n<br />\n（二）不要落單在選區暗角夜行，免生危險又失一票。<br />\n<br />\n（三）不要接受任何調查、訪問或試探，你理得我！<br />\n<br />\n（四）不要放鬆對票站票箱及點票之監察，最好聯群結隊以防出蠱惑，掉包或作廢。 <br />\n<br />\n李碧華<br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com"},{"pid":"d427316d0a28dd147111880af6b56626f52c4509","tid":1747408,"uid":68445,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T07:58:11.000Z","msg":"每一票都好重要<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n簽名檔：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hcbKZmc.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhcbKZmc.gif&h=5cafa909&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4428b7096e4197eb3978b6ed95e45946899a60a8","tid":1747408,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d427316d0a28dd147111880af6b56626f52c4509","tid":1747408,"uid":68445,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T07:58:11.000Z","msg":"每一票都好重要<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n簽名檔：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hcbKZmc.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhcbKZmc.gif&h=5cafa909&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T08:03:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26c5e16d7d8595f601431f1e688b72539da89023","tid":1747408,"uid":292007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T08:04:45.000Z","msg":"未睇入嚟睇<br />\n睇咗入嚟推<br />\n<br />\n遇到「自殺」案嘅應變指南<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1746045\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1746045</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8cbe4e850b9ef5f85182c58e77218d302f02b465","tid":1747408,"uid":288312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T08:11:33.000Z","msg":"[深度數據分析] 你知道嗎？多你一票好多<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ezEbiS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ezEbiS</a>"},{"pid":"d96c6ac6552892ab2d4bac9eb4a84d0bfe510a8c","tid":1747408,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T10:53:49.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"9e823d1bf2ffb447cd207156bb8ec848403b5c6c","tid":1747408,"uid":202895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T10:55:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">（三）要看重每一票：都有作用，有價值，眾志成城。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"affc4b33c03016b0b553fab1eaac53381115d27e","tid":1747408,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T14:44:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"63f8e2d6c6d336b00b654785e07263266a05536c","tid":1747408,"uid":303982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T15:14:44.000Z","msg":"呢啲有意義嘅po又推唔起，推埋啲冇價值嘅po，有外國嘅普通人講幾句就神咁拜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"059d051efe0ee70ded06c817c155f1004c6f000b","tid":1747408,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d427316d0a28dd147111880af6b56626f52c4509","tid":1747408,"uid":68445,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T07:58:11.000Z","msg":"每一票都好重要<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n簽名檔：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hcbKZmc.gif\" data-thumbna